{"type": "article", "id": 60279, "title": "一款简洁书桌，还配置了各种隐藏收纳空间｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-01-14T23:04:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 55942, "name": "RMDLO"}, {"id": 40818, "name": "Bernhardt Design"}, {"id": 49558, "name": "Zegen"}, {"id": 55943, "name": "Ran Merkazy"}, {"id": 55944, "name": "Freddie Camrass"}, {"id": 55945, "name": "Gražina Bočkutė"}, {"id": 55946, "name": "Thomas Pedersen"}, {"id": 39099, "name": "Oki Sato"}, {"id": 55947, "name": "Andrey Mohila"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 198, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190114203419MTL6QDIoYUim8X9e.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #5264a8; -webkit-text-stroke: #5264a8} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: #262626} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #5264a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #5264a8} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #5264a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #5264a8} span.s7 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} span.s9 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s10 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s11 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #262626; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #262626} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>DUOO Writing Desk by Andrey Mohila for Zegen</h3><p>家居品牌 Zegen 推出了一款新品办公桌 DUOO，出自设计师 Andrey Mohila 之手。</p><p>DUOO 剔除了任何不必要的装饰，仅为专心工作或是写作留存了一个干净、简洁的空间。尽管桌面采用简约设计，但它配备了贴心的小隔间来管理用户的电缆，以及收纳办公用品的抽屉和高架以容纳额外的装备。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203451PUsCLT0YG5brf1Ig.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498438\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203451LkKiPJAXCrHcpZzg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203451xjB49oRONiCEtqvb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203452Wv0qESAYK5DLMROs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203452BGW6ZedilT5fRXAs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203452r0ad6kwSmj5KtMvY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://zegen.ua/en/duoo-writing-desk\" rel=\"nofollow\">Zegen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Melt collection by Oki Sato</h3><p>日本设计品牌 Nendo 创始人佐藤大为威尼斯品牌 WonderGlass 设计了一系列铸造玻璃椅，其特点是由重力对熔融玻璃的影响形成的 U 形底座。</p><p>Melt 系列椅子由倒拱形底座组成，顶部饰有对比鲜明的平板玻璃，背面有较大的矩形玻璃。除了椅子外，该系列还包括十几件家具，这些家具都是通过重力在管道或模具上形成的。包括扶手椅、躺椅、餐桌、边桌、隔板和花瓶。佐藤大说他很惊讶看到高技能工匠自由地塑造玻璃，就像一个玩粘土的孩子。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901142035532dnMqyslhQC5ukFf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203554Uw03xfGA1eXROaLY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203554JkXjr8em2FuMwIRt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203553uqcariwY6Mb1pvLP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203554tOweE605y2kmajcu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://wonderglass.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WonderGlass</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Pederson Lounge Chair by Thomas Pedersen for Bernhardt Design</h3><p>备受赞誉的丹麦家具设计师 Thomas Pedersen 以其典型的丹麦式简约设计语言而闻名。最近他为 Bernhardt Design 品牌创作了一款名为 Pederson 的休闲椅，这是双方的第一次合作，其灵感来自于丹麦自然海岸线上的贝壳，同时结合了 Pedersen 的 3D 贴面工艺，试图通过设计中寻找舒适、耐用和个性的最佳平衡。</p><p>多年来，他一直致力于简化 3D 贴面，同时保持其个性，最终探索出了这把 Pederson 休闲椅。它采用橡木或胡桃木制成，木质饰面包括透明橡木和天然胡桃木，哑光乌木以及中间的过渡色。还有四种金属底座选项，包括铜铬合金、抛光铬合金、黑铬合金和哑光黑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203649rjGoZMwc6gP4Kkpl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655469\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203649G3RbadC4HW2tz1ou.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203649VtdkmLPzrGHBFeb9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203649qauZzFfhvYmHoOT0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203650br4FWxJnYiCuZjf0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.060938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203650dUVbnKFtf7lSwv3k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203651GbJ7jE9lhXoHfagd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.060938\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://bernhardtdesign.com/product/pedersen/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bernhardt Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Sensus by Gražina Bočkutė</h3><p>Sensus 是一种可穿戴可调导航装置，适用于盲人和视障人士。它使用红外传感器探测障碍物，并发出振动，当障碍物越来越近时，振动就会加剧。</p><p>这个装置几乎可以连接到任何东西上。它使用不同的部件，可以很容易地插入到设备中。这包括一个夹子，一个戒指，一个夹在白色手杖上的夹子和一个臂章。这些部件装在一个紧凑的盒子里，在这个盒子里，设备可以随时随地充电和携带部件。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901142037382v13QldgJVXrq9oS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901142037387I8TtDczCXfJ4Qi0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203738ut7fn6Iad9oCVyE2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901142037398kdGDFMeazWIXOYq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203739MK1YVGgx5DeRdwBW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203739Nl8aoGfV6d4wHB1e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203740v3WIlgC1wMZcemxO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://grazinabockute.wixsite.com/design/sensus?fbclid=IwAR0to4__IWE5soaP2LmHZjaRHtNlOuvihlwqd2VeAwiJUpTM8l_xhieIKNQ\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gražina Bočkutė</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>RMDLO Collapsible Colander Steamer by Ran Merkazy &amp; Freddie Camrass</h3><p>试着想象家中清洗蔬果的滤水篮，可以收成宽仅 7.5 公分的片状，并轻松吊挂收纳，是一件多么舒爽的事。</p><p>来自英国的 RMDLO 折叠蒸滤篮，具备四种“蒸、滤、倒、挂”功能，完美的收合折叠让不使用时的体面积大幅缩小，收纳不占空间之外，外出露营等户外活动也非常好携带。</p><p>RMDLO 折叠蒸滤篮采用高级 301 不锈钢制作，抗磨性优于 304 不锈钢，申请专利的 Fluid Form™，让展开与收合使用达到惊人的流畅。售价 26.56 美元，<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/RMDLO-Collapsible-Colander-Steamer-Stainless/dp/B018VR8DRK/?tag=yankodesign05-20\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203844NaGRHICJjM0W9TbO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203844ywzFbQT82R3LtV0P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203843SXQ3TrfGj2aOU1YB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019011420384534So8J2nTAsQLzfw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.632381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203845YIASRHt0w4ohNElW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.935238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203845GW38jkPay6AgtSl2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203845X6U3oOv2yDiW7lM5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190114203845n09zZfKbkBULlcMX.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.850000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>"}